    <item>
      <title>白俄罗斯在紧张局势中扩大对欧洲人的免签政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/belarus-expands-visa-free-regime-for-europeans-amid-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯盟友白俄罗斯已允许来自 35 个欧洲国家的游客通过陆地边境口岸免签证入境，该国总统亚历山大·卢卡申科试图在与西方邻国日益紧张的关系中表现出更为友好的语气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/belarus-expands-visa-free-regime-for-europeans-amid-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 13:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
